productDescription: Silver Victorian Tear BottleVictorian design inspired the style of this unique Tear Bottle. An intricate antiqued silver filigree pattern of flowers and leaves wraps around the cobalt glass bottle and also covers the cap. Each cap has a silicon plug, providing a tight seal.The tear bottle tradition has historically been a mourning tradition. They symbolize an intensely personal gift in remembrance of a loved one. Tear bottles were fairly common in Roman times, when mourners filled small glass vials or bottles with tears and placed them in burial tombs as symbols of love and respect.

productTitle: Almay Clear Complexion Acne & Blemish Spot Treatment Concealer Makeup with Salicylic Acid- Lightweight Full Coverage Hypoallergenic Fragrance-Free for Sensitive Skin 200 Light/Medium 0.3 fl oz.
productDescription: The new and improved hypoallergenic Almay Clear Complexion Concealer™ skin balancing formula works to spot treat acne and support skin’s healthy look. Ideal for acne prone skin types, oily skin, and combination skin, the lightweight, full coverage concealer targets and fights blemishes, leaving skin with a seamless soft matte finish that lasts all day. In addition to a dose of maximum strength 2% salicylic acid that helps treat and prevent future breakouts, this makeup essential is now powered by prebiotics and aloe vera. Why? Prebiotics nourish a healthy skin barrier for a well balanced complexion; soothing aloe vera moisturizes skin, which helps calm signs of irritation. The nondrying, non cakey, non comedogenic (won’t clog pores!) concealer also comes with a redesigned doe foot wand for even better application. And because Almay loves the planet as much as your skin, the cap is made with 29.7% PCR material and the card the concealer is packaged in is made of 100% sustainably sourced FSI paperboard. Formulated without added parabens, phthalates, SLS, mineral oil, DMDM Hydantoin, formaldehydes, Triclosan, and palm oils. Suitable for sensitive skin. As always, hypoallergenic. Dermatologist tested. Clean. Cruelty free. Fragrance free.

', ' AVAILABLE IN 8 SHADES: Choose from 8 vibrant shades including natural nudes, pretty pinks, and radiant reds. Every long-wearing, richly pigmented shade matches beautifully with all skin tones.  ', " CRUELTY-FREE BEAUTY: This lip pencil's luxe, matte finish creates the perfect canvas for color and the easy-glide formula ensures quick, frustration-free application. Never tested on animals.  ", ' TIPS & TRICKS: Select the shade of lipliner that best matches your chosen lipstick color. Trace the outline of your lips first, then apply lipstick to make your lips pop.
